Privacy Policy
Introduction
This Privacy Policy outlines how Maidan Official (“we,” “our,” or “us”) collects, uses, discloses, and protects your personal information when you interact with our services, website, and mobile application (“Platform”). By using our Platform, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
Information We Collect
2.1
Personal Information
: We may collect personal information, including but not limited to your name, email address, phone number, and any other information you provide to us when using our Platform.
2.2
Usage Data
: We may collect information about your use of the Platform, including your interactions with content and features, the pages you visit, and other actions you take.
How We Use Your Information
3.1
Provide Services
: We may use your information to provide you with our services, process transactions, and respond to your requests.
3.2
Improve Services
: We may use your information to understand and enhance our services, including analysing usage patterns and optimizing user experience.
3.3
Marketing
: With your consent, we may use your information to send you promotional materials and updates about our services.
Disclosure of Your Information
We may share your information with:
Service providers and third parties who assist us in providing our services.
Legal authorities when required by law, regulation, or legal process.
Business partners when you access our services through their platform.
Security of Your Information
We employ security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of data transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.
Your Choices
You have the right to:
Review, update, or delete your personal information by contacting us.
Opt-out of marketing communications by following the instructions provided in such communications.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our information practices. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on our Platform.
Top of Form:
By using our Football Pitch Booking App, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these Terms and Conditions. If you have any questions or concerns, please contact our support team for assistance.